column1: Daily Weather Observations for Castlemaine, Victoria for March 2016
Prepared at 13:03 GMT on Thursday 14 April 2016   IDCJDW3013.201603
Most observations taken from Castlemaine, but pressure from Bendigo.
Bendigo Airport is almost 40 kilometres north of Castlemaine, so the pressures will sometimes be markedly different.
Temperature, humidity, wind, cloud and rainfall observations are from Castlemaine Prison {station 088110}
Pressure observations are from Bendigo Airport {station 081123}
